snippet.title: Co OPERATION: MultiTurn (pre-alpha)
snippet.description:
Co OPERATION: MultiTurn is a comedic tactical-puzzle game for 1-4 players. We're currently pre-alpha testing. You can get a download code by joining our mailing list:
https://eepurl.com/h6o_vv
You can also get involved with our community:
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/5RSq85mQ6q
Site: https://mindfeastgames.com
Music : Sweet Tamarind by Jim Rattigan
